Croatia is now in danger of not qualifying for next year's
Olympics in Sydney. The top five teams will join Yugoslavia, which
has qualified by winning the world championship title last year.
</P>
<P>
In Pau, Spain took early control and cruised home against the
shorter Israeli team, leading by as many as 18 points.
</P>
