in the Yugoslav province of Kosovo and efforts to reconstruct the
Balkan region.
</P>
<P>
Speaking after their talks, Papandreou said that Greece was
even now accepting the Secretary-General's invitation to
participate in the New York talks as it wanted to play a leading
role in the Balkans and the future of the Balkans.
</P>
<P>
