leader in Tibet, held a head-touching ritual to bless lamas and
farmers and herdspeople who came to greet him at Deqen Pozhang,
his new palace in Xigaze.
</P>
<P>
There were more than 20,000 people lining up in the rain to
wait their turn to be touched by Erdeni Losang Qamba Lhunzhub
Qoigyijabu, the 11th Panchen Lama.
</P>
