The BSE-200 index and the U.S. dollar index were quoted
remarkably up at 410.54 and 157.64 points compared with the
previous close of 404.94 and 155.38 respectively.
</P>
<P>
Equities rose smartly with cyclical stocks hogging the
limelight on the opening day of the new account on the stock
market Monday on fresh buying by operators as well as sustained
purchases from foreign institutional investors and Indian
financial institutions. 
