Visitors and business people worldwide will learn to know more
about the city's economic achievements and high-tech development
in the fields of real estate and its medicine industry.
</P>
<P>
At the same time, two seminars on city development research and
non-governmental economic development will be hosted during the
week.
</P>
<P>
