<HEADLINE> Thai Bourse Down 11.97 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, June 28 (Xinhua) -- The Stock Exchange of Thailand
(SET) index Monday lost 11.97 points from last Friday to close at
531.88.
</P>
<P>
Some 781 million shares worth 13 billion baht (351 million U.S.
dollars) changed hands Monday.
</P>
<P>
The SET index last Friday lost 0.12 points to close at 543.85.
</P>
</TEXT>
